subject: Concussions
Wrestling
Olympic Games (2008)
Sports Injuries
lead_paragraph: Jake Deitchler, once seen as a possible Olympic medalist in Greco-Roman wrestling, retired in January because of the cumulative effects of about a dozen concussions.
